    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz001.m4a",
      "text": "ここのパンケーキは絶品でしてよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The pancakes here are simply divine.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 3.4750114440999997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 3.6750115395
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz002.m4a",
      "text": "このお店を紹介して差し上げた私に\nしっかり感謝して、じーっくり味わって……あ、ちょ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You should be deeply grateful to me for\nintroducing you to this place and savor every bite… Ah‚ hey!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 3.6750115395,
      "endTime": 11.8968708039,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 12.0902038892
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz003.m4a",
      "text": "私のクリームをとらないでくださいまし！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Don't steal my cream!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.0902038892,
      "endTime": 15.3333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 15.4482300758
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "へへーん、油断する方が悪いんだよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hehe~‚ it's your fault for letting your guard down!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 15.4482300758,
      "endTime": 19.2587288379,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 19.5120619933
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz004.m4a",
      "text": "なんで自分のパンケーキをとられないよう\n注意しないといけないんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why do I have to be on guard\nagainst having my pancake stolen!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 19.5120619933,
      "endTime": 24.0842840354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 24.2509511153
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz005.m4a",
      "text": "まったくもう、油断も隙もあったものじゃないですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Honestly‚ I can't let my guard down for a second.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.2509511153,
      "endTime": 28.597028366700002,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 28.7970264593
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "えへへ～、そんな褒めないでよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ehehe‚ you're making me blush.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 28.7970264593,
      "endTime": 33.1333330154,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz006.m4a",
      "text": "どこをどうとったら褒めていると思えるんですの！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What part of that was a compliment?!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.2230548065,
      "endTime": 36.3897213619,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 36.596387895
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "まあまあ、とりあえず食べようよ\nはい、クリーム",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Come on‚ let's eat.\nHere‚ some cream for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 36.596387895,
      "endTime": 40.4068640074,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 40.6935330392
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz007.m4a",
      "text": "どうして私が諫められているんですの……\nというか返すなら最初からとらないでくださいまし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Why am I the one being scolded…?\nAnd if you're going to give it back‚ just don't take it in the first place!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.6935330392,
      "endTime": 48.2777055742,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 48.6310362499
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz008.m4a",
      "text": "いただきます\nあ～、美味しいですわ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well then‚ let's dig in.\nAh‚ this is delicious.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 48.6310362499,
      "endTime": 54.1775667828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 54.4308951696
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんは可愛いなー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan is so cute~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 54.4308951696,
      "endTime": 58.0461348375,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 58.1061254661
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz009.m4a",
      "text": "い、いちいち言わなくていいですわよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-stop it!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 58.1061254661,
      "endTime": 61.1775314014,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 62.2908647538
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "そういえばさー、すずにゃんの小さい頃って\nどんな感じだったの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "By the way‚ what were you like\nwhen you were little?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.3575357438,
      "endTime": 68.4999989828,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 68.7365618706
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz010.m4a",
      "text": "なんですの、突然？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What's with the sudden question?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 68.7365618706,
      "endTime": 70.5311423779,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 70.7378090541
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "すずにゃんもそうだけど、みんなの昔の話って\nあんまり知らないなーって思ったんだよねー",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I realized I don't really know much about\neveryone's past‚ you know~?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.7378090541,
      "endTime": 77.9385808309,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 78.1452008247
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz011.m4a",
      "text": "言われてみればそうですわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Now that you mention it‚ you're right.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.1452008247,
      "endTime": 80.8452009201,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 81.0918670256
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz012.m4a",
      "text": "でも……私の昔話はそんなに……\n本当はもっとこう……天才的な……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But… my past isn't that…\nWell‚ it's more like… I was a genius…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.0918670256,
      "endTime": 87.8658350546,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 88.1924995342
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "あはは。いいんだよ、すずにゃん\nありのままのすずにゃんの話が聞きたいな！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ahaha‚ it's okay‚ Suzu-nyan.\nI want to hear about the real Suzu-nyan!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.1924995342,
      "endTime": 94.9237691799,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyocafe-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyocafe-00-noon",
      "startTime": 95.2237675586
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz013.m4a",
      "text": "そ、そうですか……では……みなさんには秘密ですわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-is that so…? Well then… this is a secret‚ okay?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 95.2237675586,
      "endTime": 101.5418854633,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narumiyahoom",
      "startTime": 102.6418859083
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_narudining-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "narumiyahoom",
      "startTime": 102.8752192417
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz014.m4a",
      "text": "お父様は私にとっても甘くて……\nというより、もはや溺愛していましたの",
      "translations": {
        "en": "My father was incredibly sweet to me…\nOr rather‚ he completely spoiled me.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 103.6752274433,
      "endTime": 110.09003457220001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-suzu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/extraStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01/sud_vo_adv_group_moon_02_01-suz015.m4a",
      "text": "おとうさま！　あのオモチャがほしいですわ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Daddy~! I want that toy!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 110.3033680199,
      "endTime": 113.6117353199,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mmob1",
      "speakerName": "すずの父",
      "speakerNameEn": "Suzu's",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mmob1.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "そうかそうか。よし、買ってあげよう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Okay‚ okay. Sure‚ I'll buy it for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 113.805068596,
      "endTime": 116.9517358856,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "suz",
      "speakerName": "成宮すず",
